Calculate carbon in SWDS for the Production Method

Column names with only letters come from Calc sheet, otherwise sheet is specified (need to change names)

calculatedumpcarbonproduction(Years, totalcarbonstockchange = FALSE)

Arguments

Years
years to calculate
totalcarbonstockchange
If true, returns carbon stock change, or returns data frame of intermediate calculations

Value

Either a data frame of values from Calculation spreadsheet or total carbon output

Examples
